headline: 5 Insightful Analyst Questions From Archer-Daniels-Midland’s Q4 Earnings Call
summary: Archer-Daniels-Midland faced a challenging fourth quarter, with management attributing the decline in performance to weak global agricultural trade, lower North American exports, and persistent softness in packaged food demand.
